4082:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             scan direction is forward (from lowest channel number to
4083:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Inc/stm32h7xx_ll_adc.h ****   *             highest channel number).
