1324:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   * @retval ADC group injected conversion data
1325:Drivers/STM32H7xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32h7xx_hal_adc_ex.c ****   */
